Author: MforMike
Title: [ANN][ICO]Dome PlatformğŸ”¥1500+ ETH contributedğŸ”¥ ICO LIVE
Body: Another coin with no future. Governments in Europe are making WiFi free in the public areas and continue to increase the areas with free WiFi. By the time your project spread (actually way before your project can spread), in almost everywhere, there will be free WiFi. And you are coming here with no product but with just a small interface saying that we have a cool idea, give us your money so that we can make our product like all the other ICOs on the market. Also your roadmap is couldnâ€™t be any lamer. What is that idea before the june and with one month marketing study whitepaper release? What you study in a month is like oh there is a free money on ICO thing so lets make our own and get some? Other than that let me ask you a good question; How are you planning to reach people? Without huge network of people your project would be useless so what is your plan for that? And donâ€™t come to me with â€œwe will reward people who opens their WiFi to use and other people know us since they are looking for free WiFiâ€. Why would anyone open their WiFi to public for a few penny and take the risk of those people who connect the WiFi? What if they do illegal things? And another thing is why would WiFi sharers trust you, what if you reach their privates in their computer through your program once they join WiFi sharing? Also as a person who looks for free WiFi how am i supposed to find you? And once again why would I trust you? I can generate a lot of questions like that and all make sense since your project is not solid at all. Every single day, so many ICOs popping out of thin air with a fancy website and asking for money. I hope people won't get fooled by this and other useless coins since they are ruining the trustability of good ICOs as well.

Title: [ANN][ICO]Dome PlatformğŸ”¥1500+ ETH contributedğŸ”¥ ICO LIVE

Author: MasterRadix
Title: [ANN][ICO]Dome PlatformğŸ”¥1500+ ETH contributedğŸ”¥ ICO LIVE

We are still in process of developing the region system, for now different regions = different countries, but we want to unite several small regions to make the network more organic and, I would say fair for some users.  The demo will be released in couple of days, I am sure it will give you the full description of how the platform works. Our developers are also preparing technical article which will describe the technical aspect of the platform in details.

Author: MasterRadix
Title: [ANN][ICO]Dome PlatformğŸ”¥1500+ ETH contributedğŸ”¥ ICO LIVE
Body: Hello,  At first glance, both projects look very similar, but as it was told before in comments we've approached the idea of creating the global Wi-Fi network from the point of businesses and bigger cluster of users. That will allow our platform to grow much faster and effective. Another different feature of our platform is that the connection is  free. User doesn't need to pay anything for using Wi-Fi. The system automatically rewards person/business who share their network. The amount of rewarded token depends on how many people are connected, how much traffic they use, it also depends on the popularity of the network, location and popularity of the nearby networks. This process is pretty similar to mining. We will be releasing the demo-version of our project soon as well as a technical document that will contain more information about how the system going to act, now we can say that it definitely going to happen before the ICO.

For now it is too early to talk about strategic partners, as it is mentioned in our Whitepaper, we plan to develop several partnership programs which involve marketing contracts with travel agencies, airlines, car/estate rental services etc. to increase brand awareness worldwide, but now we are concentrated on developing the app and the other technical conditions of the platform to release MVP and Alpha as soon as possible. Author: MasterRadix
Title: [ANN][ICO]Dome PlatformğŸ”¥1500+ ETH contributedğŸ”¥ ICO LIVE
Body: Hey,  First of all, thank you for your attention to Dome Platform!  The main goal of our project is to provide users with the ability to save their money on expensive 4G(LTE) data and data roaming while traveling, like you do. Everyone use internet and use Wi-Fi so the audience is wide, but like it was mentioned before and in our whitepaper, our plan is to approach the problem from the point of businesses. We've developed a special program that will allow to involve businesses into the platform by the ability to use context-basis advertisement inside the Dome Platform.This would allow to greatly increase the brand awareness, attract more users and also has been one of the variants of using DME token inside the platform.  To give you a more clear idea of how it's going to work, let's imagine that your favorite cafe or restaurant or even the office of a public company gives you the ability to use their good quality Wi-Fi network for unlimited period of time for free, just for watching a 30 second ad, would you use it instead of expensive 4G internet? In our opinion this question is rhetorical.

Author: MasterRadix
Title: [ANN][ICO]Dome PlatformğŸ”¥1500+ ETH contributedğŸ”¥ ICO LIVE
Body: WEBSITE WHITEPAPER  DEMO VIDEO    THE DOME  The Dome platform will allow user to share their Wi-Fi network and get tokens for it. Platform usage would lead people to use the Dome Platform to compensate their internet payments and even to earn from it! The creation of Dome Platform will allow users to dismiss high payments for the 4G (LTE) data and use the internet without any restrictions worldwide.    The above scheme shows the token lifecycle inside of The Dome Platform environment.   WHY USE DOME PLATFORM?  The main advantage of using Dome Platform is saving on high charges for the 4G(LTE) data usage and data roaming when you travel. Dome Platform could be used for businesses. We are developing a special business accounts that will allow users to purchase Context-based ads that will appear periodically as user using the network. The ads could be removed by an in-app adblock which could be also purchased by tokens.   Costs of 4G (LTE) data usage in developed countries    THE ESSENCE OF THE PROJECT  The idea of implementing the blockchain technology and Ethereum smart-contract into the creation of global Wi-Fi network, in our opinion, is based on a fact that people are not motivated to share their personal Wi-Fi networks. This is explained by the heavy load on the network which slows down the data rates and could result in a higher payment for the internet connection without any compensation. We offer users a platform that will allow a transparent and secure way to share and control your personal or business network using DME tokens.  APPLICATION  Log In Screen    This is how the landing screen of the application going to look. Users will be able to register using Facebook or Google account, or by email  Map   The map shows you all the available networks around you. Simply click on Wi-Fi pins and you will be able to see the information about the network and connect to it. Wi-Fi pins will be also shown when your device is offline.  Control panel   We provide and extensive functionality that could be applied to your network, including but not limited to the wallet management, business account, advertisement and more!  Network creation   Network creation and connecting. We have started of with an iOS app because this is what our lead engineers felt the most comfortable with delivering as an MVP to our potential investors. Our app makes you experience the Wi-Fi connectivity on your phone like never before. The team always sets the highest standards when we go about designing a new product and that is why our app  is on the cutting edge of technology and functionality.  In the demo weâ€™ve used the iOS 11 Beta SDK, which comes with unprecedented networking capabilities. In the new version of their operating system Apple has added a lot of functionality to the NetworkExtension framework, including the programmatic Wi-Fi apis. If youâ€™re tech savvy and a part of Apple developer program you can check out more here: https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2017/707/  What is very notable is the fact that iOS 11 is going to be released tomorrow, September 19th, which means that only starting from tomorrow people will be able to use those new APIs to modify the existing apps in the AppStore, while our application already has all of that functionality.  All the network credentials, such as SSIDs and passphrase are stored securely on our server, which means that you have the full control over the network that you share. Thanks to the new iOS frameworks, our users never have to deal with opening the settings app, copying names, memorizing passwords etc. Our application does it for you and what is the most beautiful part that weâ€™re proud of is that it just works!  When you create a network you have to be in physical proximity with the transmitter. Our app will then scan the Wi-Fi for the SSID that you specified and attempt to â€œtest-connectâ€ to your network. That will help us keep the platform more secure and avoid garbage networks on the map.  When you connect to the network, you will get the encrypted credentials from our server, which will then be used to associate with the corresponding SSID. Once you connect to the other network, the previous credentials data will be removed. This approach allows us to keep track of how many connections to each networks are happening and reward the miners fairly!  Adding business account   Business account. Be able to claim the Wi-Fi network as your business. This will enable you to use some of the more advanced features of the Dome Platform,  such as location specific advertisement, consumers analytics and additional rewards.  HOW IT WORKS?  For regular users By signing up and connecting to the platform, you automatically unblock the region (country) or several regions (depends on project development stage), where you will be able to use internet without any restrictions. Share your Wi-Fi network and get tokens, which could be traded or spent for the in-app purchases such as: unblocking new regions if you are travelling or Adblock to get rid of advertisement, etc.  For businesses Register your company in the Platform app and share your Wi-Fi, the more people use your network â€“ the more tokens you get. Trade tokens or use them in app to purchase advertisement for your business. Your advertisement will be shown to every person, who connects to your network.   CROWDSALE DETAILS   DME token sale will be open to the general public via an Ethereum Smart Contract.  Tokens deployed in total: 90,000,000 DME  Date & time: 02/10/17 - 02/11/17  We have come up with the following system of bonuses to early contributors incentivize early contributors: Bonuses: 20% first 24 hours 15% 48 hours 10% 72 hours 0% after 72-hour (3 day) bonus program.  If the reserved amount of DME for bonuses is fully used before 72 hours passed, the bonus program will be ended. If the bonus reserve wasnâ€™t used before the end of the program, all the DME tokens will be transferred to the reserve fund.  Duration of the crowdsale: 30 days  Token launch completion: Token sale would be over either when all the tokens are sold or the 30-day period is over.  Accepted currencies: Buyers during the initial sale will acquire DME in exchange for Ether (ETH), the sale will be administered by an Ethereum Smart Contract.  Exchange rate: 1 ETH = 1750 DME tokens  Token distribution: 1. 60,000,000 DME sold during the crowdsale. 2. 25,130,000 DME sent to the Dome Platform reserve fund. 3. 2,800,000 DME reserved for bonuses during the first 72 hours. 4. 270,000 DME reserved for marketing bounties and bonuses. 5. 1,800,000 DME reserved for developers and advisors.  If the sale ends without selling the full amount of 60,000,000 DME, any remaining token will be transferred to The Dome Platform reserve fund and will be available as in-app purchase once the platform is launched. The tokens from reserve will also be used for rewards to users who shared their Wi-Fi network. There wonâ€™t be any additional deployment of tokens. The number of 90,000,000 DME is final and canâ€™t be changed. DME tokens will be available for trading in a few days after the ICO end. Marketpalces will be announced within 7 days after ICO. Author: MasterRadix
Title: [ANN][ICO]Dome PlatformğŸ”¥1500+ ETH contributedğŸ”¥ ICO LIVE
Body: We are aware of WiC but we think that our project and their project target different niches of that area. WiC have been on this forum for a couple of years and we're really happy that they managed to successfully complete their presale recently. If one reads the whitepaper, one would see that our system approaches the problem from the point of businesses and larger clusters of customers (that we call regions). That introduces a lot of exciting opportunities for us to adjust prices/rewards based on supply and demand in any particular region.  And to put it simply, we offer free Wi-Fi for everyone, Wi-Fi donors are rewarded with tokens from The Dome Platform. Hopefully the whitepaper gives a pretty good idea about that.  Also to address the MVP question, our iOS engineer and designers have started to work on the demo.
